706058f-a.title: Brooklyn: Newport Street - Rockaway Avenue
706058f-a.text:
Newport Street, east from Rockaway Ave., showing in the center a 5-story
building, which is P.S. No. 164.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

706524f-c.title: Brooklyn: Rockaway Parkway - Newport Street
706524f-c.text:
(1)
Rockaway Parkway, south from Newport Street and New Lots Road,
showing from left to right in the background, the homes of Williaa F.
Ryerson and Derick ReE4e.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(2)
The same, a view along New ots Road, from the opposite directiou,
which will be Rockaway Parkway; at this point in the future.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(3)
The same, a close up of the Derick Remsen house.
March 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
